    "Sunshine": "阳光",
    "A LizardByte project": "LizardByte 项目",
    "Sunshine is a self-hosted game stream host for Moonlight. Offering low latency, cloud gaming\nserver capabilities with support for AMD, Intel, and Nvidia GPUs for hardware encoding. Software\nencoding is also available. You can connect to Sunshine from any Moonlight client on a variety\nof devices. A web UI is provided to allow configuration, and client pairing, from your favorite\nweb browser. Pair from the local server or any mobile device.": "Sunshine 是一款专为 Moonlight 设计的自托管游戏串流主机。它提供低延迟的云游戏服务器功能，支持 AMD、Intel 和 Nvidia 显卡的硬件编码，同时也提供软件编码选项。您可以通过各类设备上的 Moonlight 客户端连接到 Sunshine。通过直观的网页界面，您可以使用常用浏览器进行服务器配置和客户端配对操作，既可在本地服务器完成设置，也能通过移动设备远程实现设备绑定。",
    "Features": "特性",
    "Self-hosted": "自托管",
    "Run Sunshine on your own hardware. No need to pay monthly fees to a\ncloud gaming provider.": "您可以在自己的硬件设备上运行Sunshine，无需向云游戏服务商支付月费。",
    "Moonlight": "Moonlight",
    "Moonlight Support": "Moonlight 支持",
    "Connect to Sunshine from any Moonlight client. Moonlight is available\nfor Windows, macOS, Linux, Android, iOS, Xbox, and more. See": "从任何的 Moonlight 客户端连接至 Sunshine。Moonlight 当前支持 Windows、macOS、Linux、Android、iOS、Xbox 等平台。查看",
    "clients": "客户端",
    "for more information.": "获取更多信息。",
    "Hardware Encoding": "硬件编码",
